## 反射概述

- 反射（Reflection）是一种让程序自我检查和操作自身结构的能力
- 反射主要用于检查类、方法、属性等，并进行动态调用和访问
- 通常用于实现动态类型检查、依赖注入、序列化、测试框架等
- C++ 暂未提供内建的反射机制，但可以通过一些手段实现类似功能
- 反射可以分为运行时反射和编译期反射

## 运行时反射

- 运行时反射在程序执行过程中动态地获取类型信息并操作对象
- 它依赖于运行时的元数据和动态查找，通常会带来一定的性能开销

### RTTI (运行时类型识别)

C++ 提供的RTTI功能，包括 `typeid` 操作符和 `dynamic_cast` 操作符，可以用于运行时类型识别，但其功能有限。

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <typeinfo>

class Base 
{
public:
    virtual ~Base() {}
};

class Derived : public Base {};

int main()
{
    Base* b = new Derived();
    std::cout << "Type: " << typeid(*b).name() << std::endl;

    Base* c = new Base();
    std::cout << "Type: " << typeid(*c).name() << std::endl;

    delete b;
    delete c;
    return 0;
}
```

### 自定义类型注册和工厂模式

通过自定义类型注册系统和工厂模式，可以动态创建对象

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <string>
#include <unordered_map>
#include <functional>

class Base 
{
public:
    virtual void print() const = 0;
    virtual ~Base() {}
};

class Derived1 : public Base 
{
public:
    void print() const override 
    {
        std::cout << "Derived1" << std::endl;
    }
};

class Derived2 : public Base 
{
public:
    void print() const override 
    {
        std::cout << "Derived2" << std::endl;
    }
};

class Factory 
{
public:
    // 表示一个返回 Base* 类型指针且不接受任何参数的函数
    using CreateFunc = std::function<Base* ()>;

    static void registerClass(const std::string& className, CreateFunc func) 
    {
        getRegistry()[className] = func;
    }

    static Base* createInstance(const std::string& className) 
    {
        auto it = getRegistry().find(className);
        if (it != getRegistry().end())
        {
            return it->second();
        }
        return nullptr;
    }

private:
    static std::unordered_map<std::string, CreateFunc>& getRegistry() 
    {
        static std::unordered_map<std::string, CreateFunc> registry;
        return registry;
    }
};

#define REGISTER_CLASS(NAME) \
    static bool _##NAME##_registered = []() { \
        Factory::registerClass(#NAME, []() -> Base* { return new NAME(); }); \
        return true; \
    }();

REGISTER_CLASS(Derived1)
REGISTER_CLASS(Derived2)

int main() 
{
    Base* obj1 = Factory::createInstance("Derived1");
    if (obj1) 
    {
        obj1->print();
        delete obj1;
    }

    Base* obj2 = Factory::createInstance("Derived2");
    if (obj2)
    {
        obj2->print();
        delete obj2;
    }

    return 0;
}
```

- 工厂类负责注册类和创建对象

  - `CreateFunc` 是一个函数对象类型，表示一个返回 `Base*` 的无参函数
  - `registerClass` 函数将类名和创建对象的函数注册到静态注册表中
  - `createInstance ` 函数根据类名查找创建函数并创建对象
  - `getRegistry` 函数返回一个静态的注册表，该注册表是一个 `std::unordered_map`，将类名映射到创建函数

- 使用宏定义进行类注册

  为了方便类的注册，我们使用了一个宏 `REGISTER_CLASS`

  ```c++
  #define REGISTER_CLASS(NAME) \
      static bool _##NAME##_registered = []() { \
          Factory::registerClass(#NAME, []() -> Base* { return new NAME(); }); \
          return true; \
      }();
  ```

  这个宏定义了一个静态的布尔变量，并在变量定义时执行一个 lambda 表达式

  lambda表达式中调用`Factory::registerClass`函数，将类名和对应的创建函数注册到工厂中

- 使用模板代替宏

  可以使用模板来替代宏进行类注册，以提高代码的类型安全性和可读性

  ```c++
  template<typename T>
  static bool registerClass() 
  {
  	static_assert(std::is_base_of<Base, T>::value, "T must be derived from Base");
      std::string className = typeid(T).name();
      registerClass(className, []() -> Base* { return new T(); });
      return true;
  }
  ```

  ```c++
  bool registerDerived1 = Factory::registerClass<Derived1>();
  bool registerDerived2 = Factory::registerClass<Derived2>();
  ```

## 编译时反射

- 编译期反射（Compile-time Reflection）是在编译阶段收集和利用类型信息的能力
- 编译期反射的一个显著优势是它可以在不影响运行时性能的情况下进行类型检查和操作

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <tuple>
#include <type_traits>

template <typename T>
struct Reflect 
{
    static void print() 
    {
        std::cout << "Type: " << typeid(T).name() << std::endl;
    }
};

int main() 
{
    Reflect<int>::print();
    Reflect<double>::print();
    Reflect<std::tuple<int, double>>::print();
    return 0;
}
```

## 序列化和反序列化

- 序列化（Serialization）是将对象的状态转换为可以存储或传输的格式的过程
- 反序列化（Deserialization）则是将存储或传输的格式还原为对象的过程
- 主要用于网络通信、持久化存储和数据交换

### 运行时序列化和反序列化

运行时方案利用类型信息在运行时进行序列化和反序列化。常见方法包括使用反射或手动定义的元数据

以下是一个示例：

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <sstream>
#include <string>
#include <unordered_map>
#include <functional>
#include <vector>

// 基类和派生类定义
class Base 
{
public:
    virtual void serialize(std::ostream& os) const = 0;
    virtual void deserialize(std::istream& is) = 0;
    virtual ~Base() {}
};

class Person : public Base 
{
public:
    std::string name;
    int age;
    double height;

    void serialize(std::ostream& os) const override 
    {
        os << name << " " << age << " " << height << " ";
    }

    void deserialize(std::istream& is) override 
    {
        is >> name >> age >> height;
    }
};

// 工厂类，用于动态创建对象
class Factory 
{
public:
    using CreateFunc = std::function<Base*()>;

    static void registerClass(const std::string& className, CreateFunc func) 
    {
        getRegistry()[className] = func;
    }

    static Base* createInstance(const std::string& className) 
    {
        auto it = getRegistry().find(className);
        if (it != getRegistry().end()) 
        {
            return it->second();
        }
        return nullptr;
    }

private:
    static std::unordered_map<std::string, CreateFunc>& getRegistry() 
    {
        static std::unordered_map<std::string, CreateFunc> registry;
        return registry;
    }
};

// 宏定义，用于注册类
#define REGISTER_CLASS(NAME) \
    static bool _##NAME##_registered = []() { \
        Factory::registerClass(#NAME, []() -> Base* { return new NAME(); }); \
        return true; \
    }();

// 注册Person类
REGISTER_CLASS(Person)

// 序列化和反序列化函数
std::string serializeObject(const Base* obj, const std::string& className) 
{
    std::ostringstream oss;
    oss << className << " ";
    obj->serialize(oss);
    return oss.str();
}

Base* deserializeObject(const std::string& str) 
{
    std::istringstream iss(str);
    std::string className;
    iss >> className;
    Base* obj = Factory::createInstance(className);
    if (obj) 
    {
        obj->deserialize(iss);
    }
    return obj;
}

int main() 
{
    Person person;
    person.name = "John Doe";
    person.age = 30;
    person.height = 5.9;

    // 序列化对象
    std::string serialized = serializeObject(&person, "Person");
    std::cout << "Serialized: " << serialized << std::endl;

    // 反序列化对象
    Base* deserializedObj = deserializeObject(serialized);
    if (deserializedObj) 
    {
        Person* deserializedPerson = dynamic_cast<Person*>(deserializedObj);
        if (deserializedPerson) 
        {
            std::cout << "Deserialized: " << deserializedPerson->name << ", "
                      << deserializedPerson->age << ", "
                      << deserializedPerson->height << std::endl;
        }
        delete deserializedObj;
    }

    return 0;
}
```

### 编译时序列化和反序列化

编译期序列化和反序列化使用模板元编程在编译时生成代码，这样可以在不影响运行时性能的情况下实现序列化和反序列化。这种方法通常更高效且类型安全。

下面是一个完整的示例：

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <sstream>
#include <string>
#include <tuple>
#include <utility>

// Class Hand
class Hand 
{
public:
    int fingers;
    int strength;

    Hand() : fingers(0), strength(0) {}
    Hand(int f, int s) : fingers(f), strength(s) {}

    auto serialize() const
    {
        return std::make_tuple(fingers, strength);
    }

    template <typename Tuple>
    void deserialize(const Tuple& tuple) 
    {
        std::tie(fingers, strength) = tuple;
    }
};

// Base class Person
class Person 
{
public:
    std::string name;
    int age;
    Hand hand;

    Person() : name(""), age(0), hand() {}
    Person(const std::string& n, int a, const Hand& h) : name(n), age(a), hand(h) {}

    virtual ~Person() = default;

    auto serialize() const 
    {
        return std::tuple_cat(std::make_tuple(name, age), hand.serialize());
    }

    template <typename Tuple>
    void deserialize(const Tuple& tuple) 
    {
        std::tie(name, age, hand.fingers, hand.strength) = tuple;
    }
};

// Derived class Employee
class Employee : public Person 
{
public:
    double salary;

    Employee() : Person(), salary(0.0) {}
    Employee(const std::string& n, int a, const Hand& h, double s) : Person(n, a, h), salary(s) {}

    auto serialize() const 
    {
        return std::tuple_cat(Person::serialize(), std::make_tuple(salary));
    }

    template <typename Tuple>
    void deserialize(const Tuple& tuple) 
    {
        std::tuple<std::string, int, int, int, double> full_tuple;
        std::tie(name, age, hand.fingers, hand.strength, salary) = tuple;
    }
};

// Derived class Manager
class Manager : public Employee 
{
public:
    int team_size;

    Manager() : Employee(), team_size(0) {}
    Manager(const std::string& n, int a, const Hand& h, double s, int t) : Employee(n, a, h, s), team_size(t) {}

    auto serialize() const 
    {
        return std::tuple_cat(Employee::serialize(), std::make_tuple(team_size));
    }

    template <typename Tuple>
    void deserialize(const Tuple& tuple) 
    {
        std::tuple<std::string, int, int, int, double, int> full_tuple;
        std::tie(name, age, hand.fingers, hand.strength, salary, team_size) = tuple;
    }
};

// Serialize function
template <typename T>
std::string serialize(const T& obj) 
{
    auto data = obj.serialize();
    std::stringstream ss;
    std::apply([&ss](auto&&... args) 
        {
        ((ss << args << " "), ...);
        }, data);
    return ss.str();
}

// Deserialize helper function
template <typename T, typename Tuple, size_t... I>
void deserialize_impl(T& obj, const Tuple& tuple, std::index_sequence<I...>) 
{
    obj.deserialize(std::make_tuple(std::get<I>(tuple)...));
}

// Deserialize function
template <typename T>
T deserialize(const std::string& str) 
{
    T obj;
    std::istringstream ss(str);
    auto tuple = obj.serialize();
    std::apply([&ss](auto&&... args) 
        {
        ((ss >> args), ...);
        }, tuple);
    deserialize_impl(obj, tuple, std::make_index_sequence<std::tuple_size<decltype(tuple)>::value>{});
    return obj;
}

// Test
int main() 
{
    Hand hand(5, 10);
    Person person("John Doe", 30, hand);
    Employee employee("Jane Doe", 40, hand, 50000);
    Manager manager("Alice Smith", 50, hand, 100000, 10);

    std::string hand_serialized = serialize(hand);
    std::string person_serialized = serialize(person);
    std::string employee_serialized = serialize(employee);
    std::string manager_serialized = serialize(manager);

    std::cout << "Hand: " << hand_serialized << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Person: " << person_serialized << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Employee: " << employee_serialized << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Manager: " << manager_serialized << std::endl;

    Hand deserialized_hand = deserialize<Hand>(hand_serialized);
    Person deserialized_person = deserialize<Person>(person_serialized);
    Employee deserialized_employee = deserialize<Employee>(employee_serialized);
    Manager deserialized_manager = deserialize<Manager>(manager_serialized);

    std::cout << "Deserialized Hand: " << deserialized_hand.fingers << ", " << deserialized_hand.strength << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Deserialized Person: " << deserialized_person.name << ", " << deserialized_person.age << ", "
        << deserialized_person.hand.fingers << ", " << deserialized_person.hand.strength << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Deserialized Employee: " << deserialized_employee.name << ", " << deserialized_employee.age << ", "
        << deserialized_employee.hand.fingers << ", " << deserialized_employee.hand.strength << ", "
        << deserialized_employee.salary << std::endl;
    std::cout << "Deserialized Manager: " << deserialized_manager.name << ", " << deserialized_manager.age << ", "
        << deserialized_manager.hand.fingers << ", " << deserialized_manager.hand.strength << ", "
        << deserialized_manager.salary << ", " << deserialized_manager.team_size << std::endl;

    return 0;
}
```

- `std::string serialize(const T& obj)`

  - 序列化函数将对象 `obj` 的数据成员序列化成一个字符串

  - `obj.serialize()` 返回一个包含对象数据成员的 `std::tuple`

  - 将元组中的数据成员写入字符串流：

    ```c++
    std::apply([&ss](auto&&... args) 
    {
        ((ss << args << " "), ...);
    }, data);

    ```

    - `std::apply` 将一个函数应用于元组的元素
    - `[&ss](auto&&... args)` 是一个 lambda 表达式，捕获 `ss` 并接受可变参数
    - `((ss << args << " "), ...)` 是折叠表达式，将元组中的每个元素用空格分隔，依次写入字符串流 `ss`

- 反序列化辅助函数

  ```c++
  template <typename T, typename Tuple, size_t... I>
  void deserialize_impl(T& obj, const Tuple& tuple, std::index_sequence<I...>) 
  {
      obj.deserialize(std::make_tuple(std::get<I>(tuple)...));
  }
  ```

  这个函数辅助反序列化过程，将字符串数据填充到对象中

  - 获取元组元素的索引序列

    ```c++
    std::index_sequence<I...>
    ```

    `std::index_sequence<I...>` 用于生成元组元素的索引

  - 调用对象的反序列化函数

    ```c++
    obj.deserialize(std::make_tuple(std::get<I>(tuple)...));
    ```

    - `std::get<I>(tuple)...` 获取元组的每个元素
    - `std::make_tuple` 创建一个包含这些元素的新元组
    - `obj.deserialize` 将这个新元组传递给对象的反序列化函数，从而恢复对象的状态

- 反序列化函数

  ```c++
  template <typename T>
  T deserialize(const std::string& str) 
  {
      T obj;
      std::istringstream ss(str);
      auto tuple = obj.serialize();
      std::apply([&ss](auto&&... args) 
      {
          ((ss >> args), ...);
      }, tuple);
      deserialize_impl(obj, tuple, std::make_index_sequence<std::tuple_size<decltype(tuple)>::value>{});
      return obj;
  }
  ```

  这个函数从字符串中反序列化出对象

  - 将字符串流中的数据读入元组，跟上文的 `apply` 过程相反：

    ```c++
    std::apply([&ss](auto&&... args) 
    {
        ((ss >> args), ...);
    }, tuple);
    ```

  - 用辅助函数完成反序列化

    ```c++
    deserialize_impl(obj, tuple, std::make_index_sequence<std::tuple_size<decltype(tuple)>::value>{});
    ```

    `std::make_index_sequence<std::tuple_size<decltype(tuple)>::value>{}` 创建一个索引序列，用于访问元组的每个元素
